<DIV id="LayerMain"> 
  <h1>Welcome to Industrial Combustion Engineers, Inc.</h1>
  <h2>Your source for industrial furnaces, industrial air heaters, or industrial 
    ovens</h2>
  <p> If your heating and processing needs include industrial furnaces, industrial 
    air heaters, or industrial ovens, we hope I.C.E. proves to be your provider. 
    Please look at our <a class="reg" href="clients.html">Client Info</a> and 
    <a class="reg" href="about.html">About Us</a> pages to gain knowledge and 
    confidence in our ability to solve your problems. We hope our redesigned website 
    proves fast and easy to navigate.</p>
  <p>Whenever your process requires heating with a slant towards unique applications, 
    please call or <a class="reg" href="contactus.php#form">email</a> us! Our unique 
    location in the Midwest allows us to ship your order to any location in the 
    world. </p>
  <h3>Custom Engineered Industrial Furnaces, Air Heaters and Ovens:</h3>
  <div id="imgri"> 
    <div class="ctr"><img src="images/ICE_shop.jpg" width="180" height="126" alt="ICE shop facilities in Northwest Indiana" longdesc="ICE shop facilities in Northwest Indiana"></div>
    <br>
    Our shop in Northwest Indiana is ready to fulfill your industrial furnace, 
    industrial air heater and industrial oven needs.</div>
  <div class="padii"> 
    <p>From our high efficiency manufacturing facility in Northwest Indiana, we 
      offer you: </p>
    <ul class="special">
      <li>Precision-designed and precision-produced equipment engineered to meet 
        your specific needs;</li>
      <li>Quality &quot;brand name&quot; components; </li>
      <li>CAD drawing prints via email;</li>
      <li>One of the best turnaround times in the entire industry; </li>
      <li>On-time delivery of your order;</li>
      <li>Shipping to any location in the world; </li>
      <li>Single-source project handling &#8212; from start to finish we take 
        care of your needs; and</li>
      <li>Complete operating manual(s) shipped with each unit. </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <p>Perhaps the best way to sum things up is: <span class="red">&quot;You will 
    receive the highest overall value in process heating equipment (industrial 
    air heaters, industrial ovens and industrial furnaces) available in the market 
    today!&quot;</span> </p>
  <p>Many industries use our precision-designed products. Our <em>direct fired 
    air heaters</em> have been used in the building contractor, printing, railroad, 
    tank truck, and storage tank industries. Our <em>refractoryless air heaters</em> 
    have been used in food manufacturing, gypsum, salt industry and sand mold 
    castings. Our <em>batch ovens and conveyor ovens</em> have been used in the 
    auto after market, auto manufacturing, baking, electronic, fastener manufacturing 
    and coaters, foods, gypsum, metal finshing, pharmaceutical, trailer manufacturing, 
    and turbine manufacturing industries. Our <em>industrial furnaces</em> have 
    been used in die casting, extruding, forging, heat treating, investment casting, 
    machining, pressure casting, refractory, and stamping industries. Further 
    examples of our capabilities are detailed on our <a class="reg" href="case.html">Case 
    Studies</a> page. </p>
  <h3>Custom Built Drying Systems:</h3>
  <p><em class="red">NEW:</em> &nbsp;We're proud to announce our recent relationship 
    with Moffitt Company producer of custom built drying systems for the printing 
    and coating industries. For more information about our relationship with Moffitt 
    Company, please visit the <a class="reg" href="about_Moffitt.html">Moffitt 
    Company</a>&nbsp;web page and the <a class="reg" href="Moffitt_products.html">Moffitt 
    Products</a>&nbsp;web page.</p>
  <p style="page-break-before: always">We're honored that you're taking time to 
    review our site, and we urge you to come back regularly, for:</p>
  <ul class="special">
    <li>Convenient customer access 24 / 7 using our website; and</li>
    <li>Instant communications through our email capability.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><a class="reg" href="contactus.php#form">Contact us</a>&nbsp;today and provide 
    us with your specifications, we'll be glad to send you a quotation.</p>
